MedicationRequestRequestorSearchParameter

Parameter requestor:reference

Searches for MedicationRequest by a given Practitioner Reference uuid eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/MedicationRequest?requestor={Uuid}

ResourceMedicationRequest
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesMedicationRequest
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
